    },
    {
      "type": "markdown",
      "id": "79a19ab4ababe6df",
      "text": "APC values working with other people beyond our own network. We are aware of our own limitations as well as the power of networking. Where we lack knowledge or expertise and need to learn in order to better engage challenges, we form partnerships. In all of APC's work *we encourage people to network as a means of making other activities more sustainable*. If people share their experiences and skills they have greater value over a longer period and often create a ripple effect."
    },
